      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. It delivers a smooth, reliable ride with a healthy engine and transmission that perform exactly as they should. The exterior retains a nice luster, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. It has a solid service history and is ready to serve its next owner as a dependable daily driver.",
