    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle represents the absolute benchmark of its class, preserved in a state that mirrors its original showroom debut. Every surface, from the meticulously maintained interior to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a history of uncompromising stewardship. Mechanically superior and aesthetically pristine, this offering is intended for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
