      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible, pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, and it's been garage-kept since day one. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and looks brand new, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
