      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine with its factory individual throttle bodies and a linear power band peaking at a sharp 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically superlative, with comprehensive service records documenting a complete VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission delivers tactile, precise engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. Furthermore, the chassis has been professionally reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points, ensuring structural rigidity. This is a turn-key, analog masterpiece preserved in showroom condition for the discerning collector.",
